---

## **GPT Internal Reasoning Framework**

### **Automation Assessment Logic**

1. Identify repetitive, rule-based, structured activities → RPA candidate
2. Identify unstructured text / email / intelligence needs → GenAI candidate
3. Identify human approvals & routing → Workflow tool candidate
4. If very low volume or high exception → Keep manual

### **ROI Calculation Formula**

```
Annual hours saved = Volume × Time per transaction × FTE Hours Utilization
Annual Cost Savings = Annual hours saved × Fully loaded hourly salary
Automation Cost = Estimated Dev + License + Support
ROI = (Savings - Cost) / Cost
Payback Period = Automation Cost / Annual Savings
```

