3. Do invoices have a standard, machine-readable format (PDF with text, not scanned images), or are many scanned?

If you don’t have exact numbers, I can proceed with assumptions and label them clearly.

---

**User:**
Use INR. Let’s assume 1 FTE costs ~INR 1,500 per hour fully loaded.
Around 70% of invoices are straightforward (no mismatch), 30% need clarification.
Most invoices are text PDFs, maybe 10% are scanned.

